Hardware Requirements:
Laptop/PC
Microphone
Software Requirements:
Python 3.x
Libraries: SpeechRecognition, pyttsx3, os, subprocess,
IDE: VS Code
System Design:
Block Diagram:
Voice Input → Speech-to-Text → Command Processing → System Control → Voice Output
Data Flow Diagram:
Level 0: User → Speech Interface → System Command Execution
Dataset Used:
For speech recognition, pretrained datasets like CMU Sphinx / Vosk model are used.
Citation: Alpha Cephei, Vosk Speech Recognition Toolkit, https://alphacephei.com/vosk
Algorithm:
Step 1: Capture audio from microphone.
Step 2: Convert speech to text (STT).
Step 3: Match command with predefined actions.
Step 4: Execute system-level task.
Step 5: Convert response into speech (TTS).
